{
  "chapter": 60,
  "chapter_summary": "咸阳宫大校场举行御前比武，项少龙对阵秦国悍将王翦。比武分骑射与剑术两项。骑射环节中，项少龙大胆提议让王翦以自己为活靶射三箭，凭墨家守静心法和血浪宝剑逐一化解王翦的四枝连环铁箭，赢得全场喝彩。剑术环节，项少龙以疾风马速优势配合墨子补遗\"旋风式\"奇招，劈得王翦差点翻下马背，并脚下留情轻点其大腿。吕不韦见胜负已定，主动叫停，向庄襄王提议判为平局，两人同封太子太傅。项少龙谦辞应对，庄襄王欣然宣布。事后王翦低声致谢，项少龙以保密为约邀其共饮，二人惺惺相惜。朱姬赞叹项少龙口才，小盘对师父倍感自豪。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "秦人好武，最重英雄，此战是许胜不许败。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "吕相放心！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "左边看台那身穿黑色战服的人是邱日升，切勿忘记他的样子。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_xian",
      "speaker_name": "图先",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "应该来哩！却不知在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "内侍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "项少龙何在？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "内侍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弁将王翦何在？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_jian",
      "speaker_name": "王翦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "末将王翦！叩见我王！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wang_jian",
      "text": "死靶怎如活靶，不若王兄射在下三箭如何？我保证绝不用盾牌挡格。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_jian",
      "speaker_name": "王翦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "箭矢无情，项兄可想清楚了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_xiang_wang",
      "text": "请大王钦准！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_jian",
      "speaker_name": "王翦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "末将铁弓铁箭可贯穿任何盾牌，项兄尽管用盾又如何，小心了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_jian",
      "speaker_name": "王翦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_jian",
      "speaker_name": "王翦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "停手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_xiang_wang",
      "text": "项少龙、王翦两人无论剑技、骑术均旗鼓相当，臣下不想见他们任何一方稍有损伤，此战请大王判为不分胜负，两人同时荣任太子太傅，负起训导太子重责。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_xiang_wang",
      "speaker_name": "庄襄王",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项卿家意下如何，肯否就此罢休！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhuang_xiang_wang",
      "text": "王将军骑射盖世，剑术超群，臣下至为钦佩，吕相国这提议有若久旱里的甘露，臣下受命，甘之如饴。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_xiang_wang",
      "speaker_name": "庄襄王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "由今天起，项少龙、王翦两人同为太子太傅，不分高低，共侍太子。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "'久旱甘露'、'甘之如饴'，世上还有人比你这师父说话更动听的吗？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_jian",
      "speaker_name": "王翦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "谢谢！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wang_jian",
      "text": "这是你我间的秘密，王兄请我吃顿酒饭如何？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 60,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 265
    }
